1 Section 1. Chapter 610 of NRS is hereby amended by adding
2 thereto a new section to read as follows:
3 1. The Labor Commissioner may not issue or direct the State
4 Apprenticeship Director to issue an interim credential to an
5 apprentice in a program for a construction trade.
6 2. As used in this section, “interim credential” has the
7 meaning ascribed to it in 29 C.F.R. § 29.2.
